Trachipteridae 
<bibRefCitation author="Swainson, W." box="[440,625,1806,1832]" pageId="4" pageNumber="305" refId="ref35457" refString="Swainson, W. (1839) On the natural history and classification of fishes, amphibians, &amp; reptiles, or monocardian animals. Vol. II. Spottiswoode &amp; Co., London, vi + 448 pp. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 62140" type="book" year="1839">Swainson 1839</bibRefCitation>
